OL,3,CBristol's St Nicholas Market traders
OL,4,Ccould soon see increase in bills
OL,6,FFood and drink sellers at Bristol's St
OL,7,FNick's Market might have to pay the
OL,8,Fcouncil 15% of their turnover,
OL,9,Faccording to proposed plans.
OL,11,FIn a new Bristol City Council report
OL,12,Flooks at increasing fees paid by food
OL,13,Fand drink traders in the Glass Arcade
OL,14,Fsection of the popular city centre
OL,15,Fmarket.
OL,17,FThe report says an increase will help
OL,18,Fpay for better infrastructure and more
OL,19,Fnight markets.
