OL,3,CBristol's St Nicholas Market traders
OL,4,Ccould soon see increase in bills
OL,6,FThe market is made up of 63
OL,7,Findependent traders, with a further 50
OL,8,Ftraders in outdoor markets on Corn
OL,9,FStreet and Wine Street.
OL,11,FThe council report says: "The Glass
OL,12,FArcade has the lowest fees but this is
OL,13,Fthe most lucrative element of the
OL,14,Fmarket, with 75% of the 3.7 million
OL,15,Fvisits in 2023. It is not reasonable
OL,16,Ffor the most profitable element of the
OL,17,Fmarket to be charged the least.
