OL,3,CBristol's St Nicholas Market traders
OL,4,Ccould soon see increase in bills
OL,6,F"There is scope to invest in the
OL,7,Fmarket to provide better
OL,8,Finfrastructure for the current
OL,9,Ftraders, through operational
OL,10,Fimprovements and more effective
OL,11,Femergency repairs. It may also be
OL,12,Fpossible to put on events and night
OL,13,Fmarkets. However, this will require
OL,14,Fadditional investment which is not
OL,15,Fjustifiable when income targets are
OL,16,Fnot being achieved."
