OL,3,CBristol's St Nicholas Market traders
OL,4,Ccould soon see increase in bills
OL,6,FThe council says around half of the
OL,7,Ftraders at the market have been there
OL,8,Ffor more than 10 years, and there is a
OL,9,Fwaiting list of 21 food stalls and 13
OL,10,Fretail traders hoping to get a spot.
OL,12,FAccording to the council report,
OL,13,Fhigher fees for traders could bring in
OL,14,Fnew businesses.
OL,16,FIt says: "It appears that the current
OL,17,Flow fees are resulting in a low
OL,18,Fturnover of businesses within the
OL,19,Fmarket.
