OL,3,CBristol's St Nicholas Market traders
OL,4,Ccould soon see increase in bills
OL,6,F"Ensuring there are regular
OL,7,Fopportunities for new traders to take
OL,8,Fup, create and grow new market
OL,9,Fbusinesses is important to ensure a
OL,10,Fmixed and changing offer, encouraging
OL,11,Fcustomers to return again and again."
OL,13,FThe current weekly fees for traders at
OL,14,FSt Nicholas Market ranges from #123.93
OL,15,Ffor food and drink sellers in the
OL,16,FGlass Arcade, to #177.16 for
OL,17,Fbusinesses in the Exchange Hall.
