OL,3,CBristol's St Nicholas Market traders
OL,4,Ccould soon see increase in bills
OL,6,FThe council expects to make #646,000
OL,7,Fin income this year from market
OL,8,Ftraders - lower than its target of
OL,9,F#746,000.
OL,11,FNow the council is exploring different
OL,12,Ftypes of fee hikes, with options
OL,13,Fincluding a flat percentage increase
OL,14,Fto all fees or a 15% fee for only food
OL,15,Fand drink traders.
