OL,3,CBristol's St Nicholas Market traders
OL,4,Ccould soon see increase in bills
OL,6,FPlans to increase the fees will be
OL,7,Fdiscussed at a council meeting on
OL,8,FMonday 9 December. The council plan to
OL,9,Fconsult traders for six weeks about
OL,10,Fproposals before making any final
OL,11,Fdecisions.
